'''Alana''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|female]] who was one of the [[Handmaiden/Legends|handmaidens]], with [[Mina (handmaiden)|Mina]], of [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. She returned with her mistress, [[Annikin Starkiller]], [[R2-D2/Legends|Artoo]] and [[C-3PO/Legends|Threepio]] to the secret [[Underground Fortress]] on [[Aquilae (The Star Wars)|Aquilae]] from the [[Chatos Academy|Academy of Chatos]] at [[Yuell]], after the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] invaded the [[Aquilaean system]].

Her counterpart Mina remained behind as a decoy, since she physically resembled the young princess.

Alana was a somewhat stocky and short young adult.

